If you don't mind hearing my story...
I grew up in a family that cultivated cabbages.\! My family's the best in the business.\! I was supposed
to become the inheritor of the cabbage empire.\! However, I always dreamt of something more...\! Something...
sweet.\! In my quest, I ran into this town, whose specialty crop was the sweet potato.
I told my family that I wanted to create my own sweet potato empire!\! I wanted to have
a chain of sweet potato shops all across the world.\! They kicked me off the family for
rejecting my cabbage roots.\! But, I have not given up!
Roz-chan, I will achieve my dream!\! I just haven't had any luck...\! Even with all my
hard work, sometimes I feel like giving up.\! Today is one of those days where I feel
like packing my things and going back into the world of cabbage...
